  "question": "For \\( T - 20 = A \\times 2^{-t/b} \\), taking logs gives \\( \\log(T-20) = \\log A - \\frac{\\log 2}{b}t \\). What is the gradient of \\( \\log(T-20) \\) against \\( t \\)?",
